release <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the day</TIMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Flytrap</ENAMEX> broke declaring, "Because of confidentiality
requirements, we are unable to comment on any aspect of our work." (At the
hearing <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Starr</ENAMEX> told <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Kendall</ENAMEX> he disagreed with his own press release.)

            
