            But all is not lost.
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Kendall</ENAMEX>, the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">president</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">lawyer</ENAMEX>, not even intending a perjury trap, asked <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Starr</ENAMEX>
